Debris field.
    A large amount of asteroids are created.
    They all have similar, and fairly high, velocity.
    In the middle is a particularly valuable trinket which the player must retrieve.

Race.
    Static obstacles in the form of a race course.
    There are two to five opponents.
    There is a betting sequence before the race.
    Bet is the median-choosing-down bet, with anyone betting below that having an option to drop out.
    First to finish three courses.
    Winner takes it all.

Duel.
    There is one opponent, you need to destroy it.
